Package: ggreveal
Title: Reveal a 'ggplot' Incrementally
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Weverthon", "Machado", , "weverthonmachado@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9919-4738"))
Description: Provides functions that make it easy to reveal ggplot2 graphs incrementally. 
    The functions take a ggplot2 object and return a list of plots showing data incrementally by 
    panels, layers, groups, the values in an axis or any arbitrary aesthetic.
